WEBVTT

00:00:00.131 --> 00:00:04.815
When facing a persistent leadership challenge, consider the see, think, wonder routine.

00:00:05.255 --> 00:00:08.958
First, observe what is objectively happening in the organization.

00:00:09.399 --> 00:00:12.241
Second, analyze what the root cause might be.

00:00:12.801 --> 00:00:15.424
Third, wonder about potential solutions.

00:00:16.064 --> 00:00:25.952
This sequence is an active thinking scaffold designed to cultivate sensitivity, inclination, and the ability to deploy good thinking spontaneously when under

00:00:25.992 --> 00:00:26.373
pressure.

00:00:27.053 --> 00:00:33.703
Reflect on how applying this sequence might change the outcome of a current challenge rather than reacting impulsively.
